: "Q_661850865", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待或理解「人们容易被『帮助自己扩张自我』的人吸引，通过亲密关系将他人纳入自我」这个观点？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "自我扩张理论由心理学家 Arthur Aron 和 Eli Finkel 提出，他们认为个体有动机通过亲密关系来扩展自己的资源、观点和身份认同，从而增强自我效能感。 此外，自我扩张理论还认为，亲密关系中的满意度与个体感受到的自我扩张机会有关。随着时间的推移，如果关系能够持续提供自我扩张的机会，个体对关系的满意度可能会提高，反之则不会。 这个观点还挺能戳破「爱情泡沫」的，所以我们是否可以理解为，想要维持一段亲密关系的持久性和满意度，其实是在于「你自身的价值是否足够」呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-722f641b92978213c4ae9e50498ef67c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "26 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661850865"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIipj4mr3LhsV+EAMaCTEwOTM1NTgyMCDui960BjAAOIMBQBdyCTY2MTg1MDg2NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1722035945.606447", "card_id": "Q_662587991", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "唐诗三百首，你还记得几首啊？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-86f5c80998bfae2f3bd741a0a00b1381_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "26 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/662587991"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iipj4mr3LhsV+EAMaCTEwOTUxOTYxNiDvgYq1BjAAODxAGHIJNjYyNTg3OTkxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1722035945.606615", "card_id": "Q_661253082", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 14}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "少数民族的传统服饰中都体现了哪些美学元素？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1e6f3ae8a1cd7277be33243cce5e9ebb_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "26 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend